k} period, a mixture of vortices and wave packets is observed. This\nwork provides an insight into the heating problem in collisionless plasmas,\nfitting in the context of the new solar missions, and, especially for\n\\textit{Solar Orbiter}, which will allow an accurate magnetic connectivity\nanalysis, to link the presence of different intermittent events to the source\nregion.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 09:43:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-06"}
