 collected by smartphones\ncould play an important role in monitoring the health of existing\ntransportation infrastructure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Oct 2020 12:39:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 Nov 2020 14:37:21 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 Nov 2020 17:59:17 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 14 Jan 2022 00:43:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-17"}
