nd. Our energy yields\nare different from other published studies using the same method. This can\npresent an argument that if the compound that exploded is fuel rich ammonium\nnitrate (ANFO), then the actual mass that detonated is less than officially\nclaimed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Oct 2020 18:43:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 25 May 2021 17:22:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-20"}
